	  <concept id="id1617MD080BI"
            ditaarch:DITAArchVersion="1.3"
            class="- topic/topic concept/concept ">
		    <title class="- topic/title ">
			      <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">25.501</ph> General.</title>
		    <conbody class="- topic/body concept/conbody ">
			      <p class="- topic/p ">The contracting officer-</p>
			      <ol id="d1631e16" class="- topic/ol ">
				        <li class="- topic/li ">
					          <p id="d1645e20" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(a)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						            Must apply the evaluation procedures of this subpart to each line item of an offer unless either the offer or the solicitation specifies evaluation on a group basis (see <xref href="FAR-i1091607.dita#i1091607"
                        base="i1091607"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">25.503</xref>);</p>
				        </li>
				        <li class="- topic/li ">
					          <p id="d1645e32" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(b)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						            May rely on the offeror’s certification of end product origin when evaluating a foreign offer;</p>
				        </li>
				        <li class="- topic/li ">
					          <p id="d1645e41" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(c)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						            Must identify and reject offers of end products that are prohibited in accordance with <xref href="FAR-i1091171.dita#i1091171"
                        base="i1091171"
                        outputclass="fm:Subpart"
                        class="- topic/xref ">subpart  25.7</xref>; and</p>
				        </li>
				        <li class="- topic/li ">
					          <p id="d1645e53" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(d)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						            Must not use the Buy American statute evaluation factors prescribed in this subpart to provide a preference for one foreign offer over another foreign offer.</p>
				        </li>
			      </ol>
		    </conbody>
